fields.text: John, get the heck outta here
What about the people who don't like pizza?
I agree, but you didn't consider that fossil fuels mean cool stuff like monster trucks
So do I Wendell. We should certainly divest!

fields.actionDescription: EUSA shall book Cascada and Venga Boys alternating on weekends throughout the whole year. Additional costs shall be paid by the University's principal. In return, the principal is granted compulsory free entry till 11pm and drink vouchers worth £37.85.
fields.backgroundDescription: This new event structure would provide the University community with the opportunity to party with its principal every Saturday to classics like "Every time we touch" or "Boom, boom, boom, boom, I want you in my room".
